IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. LINEAR-SEARCH.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.

01 WS-ARRAY.
   05 WS-ARR-ITEMS    PIC 9(5) OCCURS 8 TIMES.
01 WS-TARGET          PIC 9(5) VALUE 123.
01 WS-INDEX           PIC 9(2) VALUE 1.
01 WS-FOUND           PIC X(3) VALUE 'No'.
   88 ITEM-FOUND      VALUE 'Yes'.
   88 ITEM-NOT-FOUND  VALUE 'No'.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.

MAIN-LOGIC.
    MOVE 123     TO WS-ARR-ITEMS(1)
    MOVE 152     TO WS-ARR-ITEMS(2)
    MOVE 11323   TO WS-ARR-ITEMS(3)
    MOVE 2       TO WS-ARR-ITEMS(4)
    MOVE 62      TO WS-ARR-ITEMS(5)
    MOVE 152     TO WS-ARR-ITEMS(6)
    MOVE 17      TO WS-ARR-ITEMS(7)
    MOVE 992     TO WS-ARR-ITEMS(8)

    MOVE 1 TO WS-INDEX
    MOVE 'No' TO WS-FOUND

    PERFORM UNTIL WS-INDEX > 8 OR ITEM-FOUND
        IF WS-ARR-ITEMS(WS-INDEX) = WS-TARGET
            MOVE 'Yes' TO WS-FOUND
        ELSE
            ADD 1 TO WS-INDEX
        END-IF
    END-PERFORM

    IF ITEM-FOUND
        DISPLAY "The element " WS-TARGET " was found at position " WS-INDEX
    ELSE
        DISPLAY "The element " WS-TARGET " was not found"
    END-IF

    STOP RUN.
